data.description: Presenting 'Dream Maker' - a prime investment in Navarre's coastal charm! This upscale 5-bed, 5-bath haven in the gated community of By the Sea is a rental-ready gem. Navarre, Florida's best-kept secret, boasts cool quartz sand and Gulf views that define dreamy beach living. Walk to the sound for shallow waters and perfect sunsets. The kitchen is an entertainer's dream, and the 5-bedroom layout ensures restful nights. Don't miss owning a piece of Navarre Beach - 'Dream Maker' is your ticket to beachfront bliss!
